  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add cumin seeds and cook until fragrant, about 1 minute.",
    "Add onion and cook until softened, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Add ginger and cook for another minute.",
    "Add chicken and cook until browned on all sides, about 5-6 minutes.",
    "Add curry powder and garam masala, and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Pour in coconut milk and bring to a simmer.",
